    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1933-11-16T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1933-11-16T16:00:00-05:00" n="218"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d218">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">821.51/1738: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Colombia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dawson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-11-16T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >November 16, 1933—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 5:25 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>91. My 90, November 14, 1 p.m. Sessions of Congress extended to November 21st by
                    Executive decree. House has begun debate on debt bill.</p>
                <p>Olaya has put off seeing me. It seems very evident he does not wish to discuss
                    matter.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dawson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
